tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits for this patient, including glucose metabolism, renal function, and electrolyte balance. No laboratory evidence of acute or chronic metabolic, renal, or electrolyte disturbances is present. Continued routine monitoring is recommended.
